{
  "Source": "solidot",
  "Title": "基础架构安全弹性技术指南（固件安全篇）发布",
  "Link": "https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=71555",
  "Content": "\u003cdiv class=\"p_mainnew\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca href=\"http://https://github.com/hardenedlinux\"\u003eHardenedLinux\u003c/a\u003e 写道\u003ci\u003e \u0026#34;\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e基础架构包括计算机体系、物联网设备或其他信息化设备的固件、硬件组件、单元等基础组成部分，如主板\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003eFlash\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e、显卡网卡等各类外设板卡的\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003eROM\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e，硬盘、\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003eEC\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e、主板\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003eCSME/PSP/SMU\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e等。基础架构安全性是整个系统的安全基石。如果基础架构的安全设置不当或存在高危漏洞、受到威胁，会导致整个系统的严重破坏，并且难以检测、恢复。固件的\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/406518045\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 128);\"\u003e运行级别高于操作系统内核所在的\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/406518045\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);\"\u003eRING 0\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e级，如果用户的威胁模型中包含攻击者持久化这一项，那固件安全就不可忽视，特别在\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/463621323\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e全球高级威胁防护的大趋势\u003c/a\u003e下，基础架构及平台固件属于整体防御中核心的环节，为了更好的推进行业对于基础架构整体弹性（\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003eResiliency\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e）水平，\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/515998950\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e赛博堡垒\u003c/a\u003e（\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003eHardenedVault\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e）和中科院软件所基础架构安全团队发起了一份关于\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/hardenedlinux/platform-resiliency-docs/raw/master/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BC%B9%E6%80%A7%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%89alpha%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%E7%89%88.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e平台固件安全的技术指南\u003c/a\u003e，草案版本由来自跨领域专家组的审阅\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003e，指南的alpha\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e预览版发布于\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003eHardenedLinux\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e社区（\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/hardenedlinux/platform-resiliency-docs/raw/master/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BC%B9%E6%80%A7%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%89alpha%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%E7%89%88.pdf\"\u003e下载\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/hardenedlinux/platform-resiliency-docs/raw/master/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BC%B9%E6%80%A7%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%89alpha%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%E7%89%88.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"\u003ePDF\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" lang=\"zh-CN\"\u003e）\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 27.84px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"\u003e，希望未来有兴趣的个人和机构可以继续推进。\u003c/span\u003e\u0026#34;\u003c/i\u003e\t\t\t\t\t                \u003c/div\u003e",
